    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个上传文档的架构流程图。核心是从用户发起请求，经过API Router，然后分发到具体的服务。我想把插件层和服务层分开表示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "API Router",
        "Plugins",
        "Services"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那服务层里具体是哪个服务处理上传？还有插件层，是不是有个uploader_docs插件？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S_uploader_docs",
        "P_uploader_docs"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，服务层是uploader_docs，它内部有个upload_doc方法。插件层也是uploader_docs，同名但职责不同。服务层用橙色，插件层用蓝色区分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S_uploader_docs",
        "P_uploader_docs",
        "SV class",
        "PL class"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把两个uploader_docs节点建好，服务层填橙色，插件层填蓝色。还需要一个Loader组件吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S_uploader_docs",
        "P_uploader_docs",
        "Loader"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要，Loader是数据存储层。另外User、API Router和Loader这三个用统一的浅灰色样式，边框用灰色细线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "API Router",
        "Loader",
        "DEC class"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已设置好DEC样式类。现在连关系：User到API Router是request，API Router到uploader_docs服务是dispatch，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "API Router",
        "S_uploader_docs",
        "request",
        "dispatch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。然后uploader_docs服务要连两条线：一条到Loader是load操作，另一条到插件层的uploader_docs是uses关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S_uploader_docs",
        "Loader",
        "P_uploader_docs",
        "load",
        "uses"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "连线完成。我检查一下：服务层调用插件用uses，加载数据用load。两个uploader_docs节点我都标注了upload_doc方法名。",
      "elements_involved": [
